
1   Neiteru Solomon ashetu enkaji o Laitoriani te Yerusalem, te nchumata o ldoinyo le Moria, teine wueji apa neibalunye Olaitoriani kewan te papaai lenye Daudi. Teine wueji apa netegelua Daudi, te nchumata ine apa neiutuutishoreki e Ornan ilo le Yebusi. 
2  Neiteru ninye ashet to lapa liare to lari liong'uan le nkitoria enye. 
3  Kuna apa ntemeta e Solomon te nchetata e nkaji e Nkai: ore enkadoro naa ntemat e nkaina tikitam oopishana, naa ntemat e nkaina naaudo endapasho. 
4  Ore ine wueji nejing'ieki neba anaa endapasho eina aji. Ore enkadoro oo sunta naa ntemat enkaina onom o ong'uan. Ore atua ina aji nemura te sahabu nasila. 
5  Ore ilo gilata sapuk neikodo too ltarakua nemura te sahabu nasila, neguetakino iltuka, o lpisia. 
6  Eikodo apa olaiguanani ina aji e Nkai too soito sidain oogol enkinyang'a, o te sahabu naing'uaa enkop e Paraim. 
7  Neaku etipika apa ninye sahabu atua ina aji, ing'apeta enyena, o loom lenyena o sunta enyena.


8   Neitobir sii ine wueji nesinya aisul, nenyaanyuk enkadoro enye o endapasho eina aji, naa ntemat e nkaina naaudo ake enchoto nabo, nemur ninye te sahabu nasila oo ntalantani iip ile. 
9  Ore enkiroishi oo lmushumaani naa shekeli nabo ometabaiki shekeli onom e sahabu. Nemur ninye lelo gilat le shumata te sahabu.


10   Ore teine wueji nesinya aisul nepik ilkerubi oare loo nkeek, nemur ninche te sahabu. 
11  Ore inaipuko e lelo kerubi pokira oare naa ntemat e nkaina are enkadoro. 
12  Ore enaipukoi olkerubi obo nelo atumore enaipukoi e likae kerubi te mpolos e nkaji. 
13  Ore inaipuko e kulo kerubi nebaya te nkadoro ntemat naaudo e nkaina, neitashe ake olkerubi too nkejek enyena eing'or olgos le kutukaji. 
14   Neitobir ilkarash liatua, pusi, o sinteti o loonyokie, o kitani napuyiapui neitobir ilkerubi.

